race.comment: INDY VET (5) failed to complete a hat-trick when 1.75L third to two subsequent winners at Marseille-Vivaux. Selected to register his second win from as many starts at this circuit. INTEL (2) looks a big threat arriving here on the back of a 5.5L sixth in the previously mentioned Marseille-Vivaux contest. HACKER JULRY (12) lost out by 2L placing second at Hyeres on his penultimate outing. Strong claims of registering his first victory of the year. IAKA (11) followed up a good 4.5L third at Lyon-Parilly with a 7.5L sixth at the same venue. Of note bidding to end a losing streak that dates back to February last year.
